name: <core_simd::vector::Simd<*const T, N> as core_simd::simd::ptr::const_ptr::SimdConstPtr>::with_exposed_provenance

intrinsics::simd::simd_with_exposed_prov.doc:
Creates a vector of pointers from a vector of addresses.

 `T` must be a vector of `usize`.

 `U` must be a vector of pointers, with the same length as `T`.
